Implementation of Cross Entropy Method for hyperparamter tuning
class QAOA.optimizers.CEM.CEM(epochs: int = 10, samples_per_epoch: int = 100, elite_frac: float = 0.1, processes: int = 12)¶

Implementation of Cross Entropy Method for hyperparamter tuning

epochs¶

number of epochs (default 10)

Type:

int

samples_per_epoch¶

number of samples in each epoch (default 100)

Type:

int

elite_frac¶

indicate how many top samples will be used to calculate mean and cov for next epoch - percent (default 0.1)

Type:

float

processes¶

number of processors that will be used (default cpu count)

Type:

int

n_elite¶

calulated by multiplying samples_per_epoch by elite_frac

Type:

int
